quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  25,33,"ЖҒe addantaa ma misal, si wanaa Men addanii ma Goonga kan e ko Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude firo"
  25,34,"ЖҒen mooЙ“oyteeЙ“e e dow geece muuЙ—um faade ka Jahannama, ko Й“en Й—on woni Й“uruЙ“e bonde nokkuure e Й“uruЙ“e majjude kade laawol"
  25,35,"GomЙ—ii Men okkii Muusaa Deftere nden, Men waЙ—i wonndude e makko MusiЙ—Й—o makko on Haaruuna ballo"
  25,36,"Men Daali: \"Yahee ka Й“en yimЙ“e fennuЙ“e Aayeeje Amen Й—en, Men yirbini Й“e yirbinndee"
  25,37,"E yimЙ“e Nuuhu tuma nde Й“e fennunoo NulaaЙ“e Й“en, Men yooli Й“e Men waЙ—i Й“e maande fii yimЙ“e Й“en, Men heblani tooГұooЙ“e Й“en Lepte muusuЙ—e"
  25,38,E AadinkooЙ“e Й“en e SamuudinkooЙ“e Й“en e yimЙ“e Й“unndu ndun e gire Й—uuЙ—uЙ—e hakkunde Й—um
  25,39,"Gooto kala e maЙ“e Men piyani Й—um mise, gooto kala e maЙ“Й“e men halki Й—um halkugol"
  25,40,"GomЙ—ii Й“e arii e nden saare toЙ“aande toЙ“o bonngo. Kaa Й“e laataaki hiЙ“e yi'a Й—e? Ko woni, Й“e laatinoke Й“e jortaaki Immotal"
  25,41,"Si Й“e yi'ii ma, Й“e jogitotaako ma si wanaa jalnori. Enee, ko oo Alla Immini NulaaЙ—o"
  25,42,Fii kala hari o Й“adike(Й—esi) majjinnde en gaayi reweteeЙ—i me'en Й—in si tawiino wanaa ko muГұГұi Й—en kon e dow majji. Aray Й“e anndoyat tuma Й“e yi'ata Lepte Й—en ko hommbo Й“urЙ—o majjude laawol
  25,43,"Enee, a tinii on jogitiiЙ—o reweteeЙ—o makko on beleeЙ—e makko Й—en. E hara ko an laatotoo e dow makko fawtiiЙ—o"
